    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Calidius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cam</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sever</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> item optio <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>decur</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Alpin</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>item |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apoll</abbr><ex>inaris</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> LVIII <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXXIIII <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Calidius fratri <lb n="9"/>posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zeile 1: T mit Überlänge, V u. S verschlungen; Zeile 8: TR-Ligatur. Unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes zweigeteiltes Sockelrelief, im oberen lorica hamata oder squamata, vitis und Helm (Typ Hagenau oder Weisenau) mit crista transversa als Kennzeichen des Centurionats, Beinschienen (ocreae) mit Masken; im unteren Feld Pferd mit calo in lorica hamata, tunica, paenula. (B): Z. 4: Lőrincz: dec(urio).</p>
            </div>
